{"tha-ap155:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap155:0.2":"Bandhujivakavagga ","tha-ap155:0.3":"Vithisammajjakattheraapadana ","tha-ap155:1.1":"“Udentam sataramsimva, ","tha-ap155:1.2":"pitaramsimva bhanumam; ","tha-ap155:1.3":"Pannarase yatha candam, ","tha-ap155:1.4":"niyyantam lokanayakam. ","tha-ap155:2.1":"Atthasatthisahassani, ","tha-ap155:2.2":"sabbe khinasava ahum; ","tha-ap155:2.3":"Parivarimsu sambuddham, ","tha-ap155:2.4":"dvipadindam narasabham. ","tha-ap155:3.1":"Sammajjitvana tam vithim, ","tha-ap155:3.2":"niyyante lokanayake; ","tha-ap155:3.3":"Ussapesim dhajam tattha, ","tha-ap155:3.4":"vippasannena cetasa. ","tha-ap155:4.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap155:4.2":"yam dhajam abhiropayim; ","tha-ap155:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap155:4.4":"dhajadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap155:5.1":"Ito catutthake kappe, ","tha-ap155:5.2":"rajahosim mahabbalo; ","tha-ap155:5.3":"Sabbakarena sampanno, ","tha-ap155:5.4":"sudhajo iti vissuto. ","tha-ap155:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap155:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap155:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap155:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma vithisammajjako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap155:8.1":"Vithisammajjakattherassapadanam tatiyam. "}